        private static final Singleton INSTANCE = new Singleton();
    }

    public static Singleton getInstance() {
        return SingletonHelper.INSTANCE;
    }
}
Why this is great

вњ” Lazy initialization
вњ” Thread safe
вњ” No synchronization cost
вњ” Clean code

This is often considered the best Java singleton implementation.

